China (CPC) on Major Issues Concerning the Reform and Development
of State-owned Enterprises, adopted at the 4th Plenum of the 15th
CPC Central Committee on September 22, 1999, contains guidelines
for the reform and growth of SOEs and must be implemented, Jiang
said.
</P>
<P>
