chairman of the Central Military Commission, made the comment
during an inspection tour of China's largest commercial center,
Shanghai, September 23-28.
</P>
<P>
He noted that Shanghai has made new achievements in ethical and
material progress, as well as city construction, thanks the
efforts of local officials and people in their timely and earnest
implementation of the CPC Central Committee's guidelines and
policies.
</P>
<P>
He asked local officials to emancipate the mind, seek truth
from facts, and continue to promote social and economic progress.
</P>
<P>
Jiang visited a number of factories, schools and living
quarters in the city, which is in full swing to celebrate the
upcoming National Day on October 1.
